1.0.0.name: wordpress/google-maps-anywhere
1.0.0.description:
Add Google Maps to your posts and pages.(Only for WordPress 2.5+) This plugin allows you to easily insert Google Maps and Street View into your blog.

Localization

"Google Maps Anywhere" has been translated into languages. Our thanks and appreciation must go to the following for their contributions:

  • Belorussian (by) - Marcis Gasuns
  • Bulgarian (bg_BG) - Web Geek
  • Croatian (hr) - Marijan Rajić
  • Dutch (nl_NL) - Rene
  • German (de_DE) - Rian Klijn
  • Japanese (ja) - OKAMOTO Wataru (plugin author)
  • Polish (pl) - Barbara Muszko
  • Romanian (ro_RO) -
